('601/7345/2','NETK3-06A','Inspection, Testing and Commissioning',5,'Understand the requirements for testing before circuits are energised.','5.5','State the effects on insulation resistance values that the following can have: a) Cables connected in parallel; b) Variations in cable length.'),
