('601/7345/2','NETK3-06A','Inspection, Testing and Commissioning',6,'Understand the requirements for testing energised installations.','6.6','Specify the methods for determining prospective fault current.'),
('601/7345/2','NETK3-06A','Inspection, Testing and Commissioning',6,'Understand the requirements for testing energised installations.','6.7','Verify the suitability of protective devices for prospective fault currents.'),
