('601/7345/2','NETK3-07','Understand Fault Diagnosis and Rectification',6,'Perform fault diagnosis.','6.1','Follow safe working procedures.'),
('601/7345/2','NETK3-07','Understand Fault Diagnosis and Rectification',6,'Perform fault diagnosis.','6.2','Evaluate and apply appropriate fault diagnosis methods and techniques.'),
('601/7345/2','NETK3-07','Understand Fault Diagnosis and Rectification',6,'Perform fault diagnosis.','6.3','Diagnose electrical faults using engineering decision and evaluation of symptoms and findings.'),
('601/7345/2','NETK3-07','Understand Fault Diagnosis and Rectification',6,'Perform fault diagnosis.','6.4','Recommend the appropriate action/s to correct the fault.');
